30. To March by the Flank. Being in march, the command is: 1. <hi rend="underline">By the Right (Left) Flank</hi>, 2. <hi rend="underline">MARCH</hi>. At the command <hi rend="underline">MARCH</hi>, given as the right (left) foot strikes the ground, advance and plant the left (right) foot, face the right (left) in marching on the ball of the left (right) foot, and step off in the new direction with the right (left) foot with a full 30-inch step.

