These instructions having been carried out, the band returned to band formation. Then maneuvered into "6 X 16" (page 18). Then the band formed "HUSKERS" following instructions on page 23, figure 14. The band commenced playing <hi rend="underline">There Is No Place Like Nebraska</hi>, then returned to "6 X 16". This is number 6 on the game plan.

